## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **linaclotide Linzess 2012** = first FDA GC-C agonist — IBS-C + CIC. 14-mer disulfide-constrained peptide. pro-secretory + visceral pain reduction dual mechanism. quantum-VQE 의 GC-C extracellular domain 직접 fit.
2. **plecanatide Trulance 2017** = second GC-C agonist — uroguanylin-mimetic (pH-sensitive). IBS-C + CIC. linaclotide 의 next-gen comparator.
3. **lubiprostone Amitiza 2008** = first FDA ClC-2 — IBS-C + CIC + opioid-induced constipation. PG E1 derivative. ClC-2 selective activator.
4. **prucalopride Motegrity 2018** = first FDA 5-HT4 agonist for CIC (US — EU 2009). cisapride/tegaserod 의 cardiac off-target 회피 — selective 5-HT4 paradigm.
5. **tenapanor Ibsrela 2019 + 2023 hyperphosphatemia** = first FDA NHE3 inhibitor — IBS-C + 2023 dialysis hyperphos cross-link (cross-chronic_kidney_disease_specific). non-absorbed gut-luminal.
6. **alosetron Lotronex 2000 REMS** = first 5-HT3 antagonist for IBS-D — ischemic colitis 위험 → 2000 withdrawal → 2002 REMS reintroduction. severe IBS-D women only.
7. **eluxadoline Viberzi 2015** = mixed μ/κ-OR agonist + δ-OR antagonist IBS-D. sphincter Oddi spasm → no-cholecystectomy contraindication. selective gut peripheral.
8. **rifaximin Xifaxan 2015 IBS-D** = first FDA non-systemic antibiotic for IBS-D — paradigm + HE (hepatic encephalopathy) cross-link. microbiome modulation 명시 + non-systemic + 14-day course.
9. **SSRI/TCA + antispasmodic (dicyclomine/hyoscyamine/peppermint oil) + low-FODMAP + 한국 mebeverine** = 만성 off-label + OTC + non-pharm 1L. Rome IV 진단 + 임상 standard-of-care.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, IBS + FD + CIC 임상 의미 한정.

